  <li>A minified <code>.json</code> file in your project repository.</li>
  <li>A database export or log entry.</li>
  <li>A colleague's Slack or email message.</li>
</ol>

<p>Copy the entire JSON string to your clipboard. Make sure you grab the complete text — partial JSON will trigger a parse error.</p>

